###Setup
###1. Create group
###2. Create 2 users
###3. Create 3 completed tasks
###4. Get group rankings

@baseurl = http://localhost:5000/api

@groupId = 69f11342ce66b7121aec7c8d
@demon1Id = 69f1133dce66b7121aec7c89
@tenzId = 69f11340ce66b7121aec7c8b
@demonFirstTaskId = 69f116edce66b7121aec7cb5
@demonSecondTaskId = 69f1163ace66b7121aec7cac
@tenzTaskId = 69f11599ce66b7121aec7ca5

###1.
POST {{baseurl}}/groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "groupName": "Roommates 343",
    "groupGoal": "We promise to complete our chores on time"
}

